These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, whist, monopoly, snooker
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, puzzles, writing
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, journalist, manager, snookercher
City: paris, hamburg, new-york, berlin
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, rugby, skiing
 1. the snookercher is on the far right##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is the person traveling to paris##1
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person playing snooker is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the manager is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person traveling to berlin##2
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is between the manager and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the snookercher is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Game      | snooker        | whist       | monopoly  | backgammon |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | fishing      | puzzles   | writing     |
| Job           | journalist | entrepreneur | manager   | snookercher     |
| City   | hamburg    | new-york         | paris | berlin         |
| Sport         | skiing     | baseball     | climbing  | rugby       |

