.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, cabbage, garlic, radish
4 different games are played: domino, canasta, go, poker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk, gospel
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, malaysian, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, train
 1. the german is between the person playing go and the person driving the bike##2
 2. the pakistani is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person playing poker is on the left of the canadian##1
 4. the german is between the person eating kiwi and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the fan of disco is the person eating cabbage##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 7. the person playing canasta is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching action movies and the person playing poker##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person playing poker##1
10. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
11. the fan of disco is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
13. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
14. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Food      | radish    | cabbage       | garlic   | kiwi |
| Game         | domino     | go   | poker    | canasta  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel | thriller   | western     |
